    narr:childCount "146"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "c354f003fe2a54a8d5d3268a64e6f8923cccb163" ;
    narr:narration """The hub traces aswritten's positioning from a developer-first enterprise tool to a layered thesis about expertise installation as a new category of knowledge distribution. The [three-era knowledge framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TrustedInformationEra) — books, search, curated expertise installation — was crystallized in Mar 2026, with [the category name itself refined](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise) by Mar 31 when 'curated' was dropped as redundant. Market targeting shifted from enterprise to [SMB as primary on Mar 12](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_SMBBiggerThanDevs), then extended to [B2C individuals on Mar 17](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_B2CPivot) when both Scarlet and Tony independently converged on solopreneurs and small businesses as the volume play. By May 21 the [tier-continuum resolution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TierContinuumNotDistinctMarkets) reframed Expert/Team/Org as one use case varying only by how many people write to the perspective, holding B2C and enterprise signal simultaneously. The [steering-as-genus frame](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SteeringDecisionProcess) (May 26) unified all three use cases: aswritten is always [the memory the steering runs on](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AswrittenIsMemorySubstrate), never the loop. Architecture differentiation rests on [flat RAG creating attention dilution](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_ArchitectureGap) versus narrative ontology with conviction levels. The [perspective-vs-information distinction](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveVsInformation) — modules install how to interpret, not just what to know — anchors the category claim against search and RAG. GTM evolved through [consulting-as-onboarding](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingAsOnboarding), the [side-door GTM pattern](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Insight_SideDoorGTM), and by Jul 15 the [consulting-is-me-using-the-product](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingIsMeUsingProduct) inversion — the client never touches the tool. Fundraising moved from YC Feb rejection (top 10%) through [the enterprise customer as first paying enterprise team](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_EnterpriseCustomerFirstEnterpriseTeamTrial) to a [Jul 2 traction inflection](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_FundraisingTractionInflection_20260625) with a Jul 26 YC reapplication deadline. The [anti-monoculture amplifier frame](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiMonocultureAmplifier) (Jul 1) and [model-as-OS / perspective-as-application](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ModelAsOS) (Jul 2) represent the most recent positioning extensions, with the [CEO context-server reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CEOContextServerReframe) and [three demotions](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TranscriptDemotionFrictionNotValue) (Jul 15) the latest refinements. The [bounded-domain fidelity argument](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BoundedDomainFidelityArgument) (Mar 19) and [matching-search reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_MatchingSearchReframe) (Apr 24) extend the thesis into expertise modules and practitioner marketplaces respectively.""" ;
